Explore Azure Cosmos DB
Key benefits
Azure Cosmos DB, a fully managed NoSQL database, offers several key benefits, including low latency, elastic scalability, defined data consistency, and high availability.
It supports global distribution, allowing databases to be placed close to users worldwide for reduced latency. With its multi-master replication protocol, every region supports
writes and reads, ensuring unlimited scalability and 99.999% availability globally. 

Azure Cosmos DB enables near real-time reads and writes across chosen regions, with automatic handling of data replication and high availability even in the event of regional outages.
